Package com.hhstechgroup.tests.regressionBaseline.iv_ORPEnrollment

This Package contains test classes covering all the test stories for ORP Enrollments.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ORPProviderAppealApprovalProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a denied ORP and appeals and approves it.
    ORPProviderAppealDenialProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a denied ORP and appeals and deny it.
    ORPProviderCoCAndAppealApprovalProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a Coc denied of an ORP provider and appeals and approve it.
    ORPProviderCoCDenyProcessTest
    This method contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved ORP provider, Creates and denies an identifying information CoC.
    ORPProviderCoCProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved ORP provider, Creates and approves an alternate email change CoC.
    ORPProviderCreateAndApproveSiteVisitTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved ORP provider and creates and approves site visit.
    ORPProviderDenyTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to register a new Provider and, creates and Denies an ORP enrollment.
    ORPProviderPaymentFeeVerificationTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to register a new Provider, creates and submits an ORP enrollment.
    ORPProviderPreConditionSetup
    This test class sets the Systems Option configuration for orp Provider.
    ORPProviderReenrollmentProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved ORP provider, Terminates, re-enrolls and approves the enrollment
    ORPProviderRegistrationAndSubmissionTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to register a new Provider and, creates and submits an ORP enrollment.
    ORPProviderRequestForAdditionalInformationAndDenyTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an ORP provider enrollment and requests for additional information and denies the enrollment
    ORPProviderRetroActiveAdjustmentApprovalTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a submitted ORP enrollment and approves the enrollment retroactively.
    ORPProviderRetroActiveRegistrationAndSubmissionTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to register a new Provider, Creates and submits an ORP enrollment retroactively.
    ORPProviderSubmitScreeningTest
    This class contains a test that performs under screens an ORP enrollment using a data provider
    ORPProviderTerminateSuspendReactiveProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved ORP provider, Suspends, terminates and reactive.
    ORPProviderVerifyDocumentReviewTest
    This class contains a test that does the document review of an ORP enrollment using a data provider.
